OL,3,CRogue builders exposed by voice note
OL,4,Cin #37K roof scam
OL,6,FTwo rogue traders who conned a
OL,7,Fpensioner out of #37,000 for
OL,8,F"shockingly poor" roof repairs worth
OL,9,Fjust #3,000 have been jailed.
OL,11,FTom Lee, 39, and Freddy Young, 27,
OL,12,Ftargeted a man in his mid-60s at his
OL,13,Fhome in Crawshawbooth, Rossendale,
OL,14,Fpressuring him for repeated payments
OL,15,Fas they carried out shoddy and
OL,16,Foverpriced work.
OL,18,FPreston Crown Court heard how the scam
OL,19,Fonly came to light when the victim's
OL,20,Fbank raised concerns over large cash
OL,21,Fwithdrawals and contacted police.
