OL,3,CRogue builders exposed by voice note
OL,4,Cin #37K roof scam
OL,6,FVoice notes recovered from Lee's phone
OL,7,Fincluded a contact of Lee talking
OL,8,Fabout the victim, saying: "This job,
OL,9,Flove it Tom, absolutely love it.
OL,10,FThere's loads of lemons about."
OL,12,FAn expert survey later found that the
OL,13,Froofing work was not only grossly
OL,14,Foverpriced but also described as
OL,15,F"shockingly poor" in quality.
OL,17,FThe victim was later forced to pay an
OL,18,Fadditional #15,000 to have the roof
OL,19,Fproperly repaired.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
