OL,3,CRogue builders exposed by voice note
OL,4,Cin #37K roof scam
OL,6,FThe victim handed over #400 in cash
OL,7,Fimmediately and then went to the bank
OL,8,Fto withdraw the remainder.
OL,10,FAfter the bank contacted police,
OL,11,Fofficers went to the house and found
OL,12,Fthree men working there ` Young and
OL,13,Ftwo others.
OL,15,FA fourth man, believed to be Lee, left
OL,16,Fprior to police arriving.
OL,18,FAn expert witness examined the work
OL,19,Fcarried out on the roof, valuing it at
OL,20,F#3,000, even though the victim had
OL,21,Fpaid out #37,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
