OL,3,CRogue builders exposed by voice note
OL,4,Cin #37K roof scam
OL,6,FFor the roof to be repaired properly
OL,7,Fafter Lee's and Young's botched work,
OL,8,Fcost the victim #15,000.
OL,10,FAt the sentencing hearing, the victim
OL,11,Fread a statement to the court.
OL,13,FHe said: "After the incident involving
OL,14,FTom Lee and Freddy Young I was left
OL,15,Fwithout a watertight roof for about
OL,16,Fthree months. There were water leaks
OL,17,Fin the attic which I tried to catch in
OL,18,Fbuckets and saucepans and water
OL,19,Fdripped from the upstairs light
OL,20,Ffittings."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
