OL,3,CRogue builders exposed by voice note
OL,4,Cin #37K roof scam
OL,6,F"I was at the mercy of bad weather,
OL,7,Fwind and storms and it snowed towards
OL,8,FChristmas. Loads of rubbish was left
OL,9,Fon the front lawn consisting of a pile
OL,10,Fof broken roof slates and rubble,
OL,11,Fmaking access very difficult."
OL,13,FHe continued: "All the work done by
OL,14,FTom Lee and Freddy Young was shoddy
OL,15,Fand had to be removed before the new
OL,16,Froofer could start. Some of the roof
OL,17,Fbatons were not nailed down and none
OL,18,Fof the roof tiles were nailed down."
