OL,3,CRogue builders exposed by voice note
OL,4,Cin #37K roof scam
OL,6,F"The edge tiles were not trimmed down
OL,7,Fproperly and there were no ridge
OL,8,Ftiles. If there had been high winds,
OL,9,Fthe roof would probably have blown
OL,10,Foff."
OL,12,F"I welcome the prison sentences which
OL,13,Fthe judge and I hope sends out the
OL,14,Fmessage that offences of this nature
OL,15,Fwill not be tolerated by the police
OL,16,Fand courts."
OL,18,FLee, of Lower Eccleshill Road, Darwen,
OL,19,Fand Young, of Heys Lane,
OL,20,FOswaldtwistle, pleaded guilty to fraud
OL,21,Fby false representation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
